    "abstract": "<jats:title>ABSTRACT</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Social distancing restrictions were lifted in Georgia, USA before the daily new Covid-19 cases were significantly reduced below the peak. In this paper we show through numerical analysis the disastrous consequence of this action resulting in a second peak of daily cases which caused additional fatalities.</jats:p>",
